name: POWERGEMZ_00
description:
There are only nine POWERGEMZ in the universe. The Knights Of Saturn's legends depict how in ancient times humans could achieve interdimensional travel by holding one POWERGEM in their hands, if they were ever to find one.


This is the first drop of POWERGEMZ, a series of 10 OBJKTS featuring one OBJKT of 90 editions including all nine crystals and nine unique editions featuring each of the nine crystals.
